    "text": "This translation key is used for the label of a toggle button that enables or disables authentication settings, typically found in SMTP settings. The text appears as a button label and is labeled as \"Authentication\" to indicate its purpose. Translators should focus on providing a clear and concise description of this setting within the context of email account management.",
    "is_auto": true,
    "updated_at": "2025-05-20T09:37:18.451Z"
  },
  "usage": [
